build_era5_request      Builds a request compatible with the CDS for
                        all microclimate relevant climate variables.
extract_clim            Produces hourly data for a single location
                        ready for use with 'microclima::runauto'.
extract_precip          Produces daily or hourly precipitation data for
                        a single location ready for use with
                        'microclima::runauto'.
request_era5            Submit request(s) to CDS for ERA5 data download
